(
<figureCitation id="130BF280404DFFCBE2DA050E37DFF8B8" box="[159,245,1797,1822]" captionStart="FIGURE 18" captionStartId="24.[151,250,1493,1515]" captionTargetBox="[202,1393,758,1479]" captionTargetId="figure@24.[193,1402,751,1483]" captionTargetPageId="24" captionText="FIGURE 18. Pleurotrocha fontanetoi sp. nov. A. Female, dorsal; B. eye, female; C. male, dorsal; D. toe, female, lateral; E. toes, female, dorsal; F. trophi, complete set, ventral; G. incus, lateral; H. left malleus, outer view; I. right malleus, outer view. Scale bars: A, C: 50 µm; D − I: 10 µm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/240574/files/figure.png" pageId="22" pageNumber="173">Figs 18</figureCitation>
