<paragraph id="8B8FEE054043FFC5E2820444338EF92A" blockId="24.[151,1436,1615,2037]" pageId="24" pageNumber="175">
<emphasis id="B94432174043FFC5E2820444369CF9CE" bold="true" box="[199,438,1615,1640]" pageId="24" pageNumber="175">Description of male.</emphasis>
Male more or less similar in habitus to female, with small head, oval trunk, and long foot composed of 
<emphasis id="B94432174043FFC5E368047E366AF92A" box="[301,320,1653,1676]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="175">c.</emphasis>
